{"tid":1575356,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪利諾學生同舊生登報，喻校友余黎青萍聆聽訴求忠於真理","createTime":"2019-09-17T00:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T09:31:22.000Z","uid":285729,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"51a550162822f28b11aba083716e99a74d3805a2","tid":1575356,"uid":285729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T00:00:14.000Z","msg":"近八百名瑪利諾修院學校（中學部）舊生及學生不滿校友余黎青萍女士近期就警察執法及社會運動發表之言論，今日（9月17日）於多份中、英文報章刊登聯署信。<br />\n<br />\n一眾校友在公開信末段懇請她秉持校訓，正視警察濫權、承認監警會的不足、以及聆聽民間五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n除了信件外，英文版設計圖亦見心思，特免去「Carrying truth」中的「y」，意指現時余黎青萍（Helen Yu）未盡其責追求真理，校友望她能虛心聆聽、早日還原真相。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiViees.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkiViees.jpg&h=e4071a57&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vbvRzet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvbvRzet.jpg&h=1d9c2d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#ToHomeToCountryToTheWorld<br />\n#LetterToHelenYu<br />\n#HongKongProtests"},{"pid":"e74751e97ef9af83b6e8cfc53c1e0012c950064d","tid":1575356,"uid":285729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T00:03:29.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed409a3a2dbd38a2510ba1221d5ce87ca8dc17d1","tid":1575356,"uid":53191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T07:33:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79a662fee93454a984df3ed1b62a7d702debd033","tid":1575356,"uid":46886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:29:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e425df8f026252b9b4665f8667db6c56c42e952","tid":1575356,"uid":230321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"}]}